data.title: List of top George Washington University Alumni Founded Companies
data.meta_description: Organizations founded by graduates of George Washington University.
data.text:
George Washington University is a co-educational research university that provides higher education services.

This list of organizations founded by graduates of George Washington University provides data on their funding history, investment activities, and acquisition trends. Insights about top trending companies, startups, investments and M&A

activities, notable investors of these companies, their management team, and recent news are also included.
